      "description": "This vehicle is presented in impeccable, showroom-state condition, representing the zenith of automotive preservation. The exterior maintains a flawless, mirror-like finish, while the interior remains entirely free of wear, reflecting a standard of maintenance that is truly exemplary. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is an uncompromising opportunity to acquire a vehicle that is indistinguishable from its original delivery state.",
